data.description:
Welcome to your own piece of countryside paradise! This move in ready, one-level country home is a true gem, nestled on over 8 acres of picturesque land. Conveniently located, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Step inside and be greeted by the warmth of natural woodwork with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, including a master bedroom with a private bath. This home has great country views with a back sunroom and front deck. Efficiency meets coziness with in floor heat for those chilly evenings. Plus, the attached double garage ensures you have plenty of
room for your vehicles and projects. Need extra storage? No problem! The 24x26 pole building has you covered. Don't miss the opportunity to make this slice of paradise yours and start living the easy country life you've always imagined. Schedule your showing today!
